{"General": {"Code": "PUGBY", "Type": "Common Stock", "Name": "Puig Brands SA", "Exchange": "NYSE", "CurrencyCode": "USD", "CurrencyName": "US Dollar", "CurrencySymbol": "$", "CountryName": "USA", "CountryISO": "US", "OpenFigi": "BBG01NPSN7P1", "ISIN": "US74535L1026", "LEI": null, "PrimaryTicker": null, "CUSIP": null, "CIK": null, "EmployerIdNumber": null, "FiscalYearEnd": "December", "IPODate": null, "InternationalDomestic": null, "Sector": "Consumer Defensive", "Industry": "Household & Personal Products", "GicSector": null, "GicGroup": null, "GicIndustry": null, "GicSubIndustry": null, "HomeCategory": "ADR", "IsDelisted": false, "Description": "Puig Brands, S.A. operates in the beauty and fashion industry in Europe, the Middle East, Africa, the Americas, and the Asia-Pacific. The company operates through three segments: Fragrance and Fashion, Makeup, and Skincare. The Fragrance and Fashion segment designs, develops, and markets fragrances in various forms, including eau de parfum sprays and colognes, lotions, powders, creams, candles, and soaps, that are based on a particular fragrance, as well as clothing, footwear and accessories under the Carolina Herrera, Jean Paul Gaultier, Nina Ricci, Rabanne, Byredo, Christian Louboutin, Dries Van Noten, L'Artisan Parfumeur, Penhaligon's, Adolfo Dom\u00ednguez, and Banderas brands. The Makeup segment engages in the creation, marketing, and sale of a range of cosmetic products, such as foundations, concealers, lipsticks, lip glosses, eyeliners, blushes, mascaras, and eyeshadows under the Carolina Herrera, Charlotte Tilbury, Rabanne, Byredo, Christian Louboutin, and Dries Van Noten brands. The Skincare segment offers cleansers, toners, moisturizers, serums, body care, exfoliators, acne, and oil correctors, facial masks, and sun care products under the Uriage, Apivita, Dr.Barbara Sturm, Kama Ayurveda, Loto del Sur, and Charlotte Tilbury brands. It sells its products in department stores, warehouses, pharmacies, drug stores, travel retail, spas, and Puig's own shops through digital channels, brands' own e-commerce, and distributors. The company was incorporated in 1914 and is based in Barcelona, Spain. Puig Brands, S.A. is a subsidiary of Puig, S.L.", "Address": "Puig Tower 2, Barcelona, Spain, 08902", "AddressData": {"Street": "Puig Tower 2", "City": "Barcelona", "Country": "Spain", "ZIP": "08902"}, "Listings": {}, "Officers": {"0": {"Name": "Mr. Marc  Puig Guasch", "Title": "Executive Chairman of the Board", "YearBorn": "1962"}, "1": {"Name": "Mr. Jose Manuel Albesa Muniesa", "Title": "Chief Executive Officer", "YearBorn": "1968"}, "2": {"Name": "Mr. Miquel Angel Serra", "Title": "Chief Financial Officer", "YearBorn": "NA"}, "3": {"Name": "Mr. Javierr Bach Kutschruetter", "Title": "Chief Operating Officer", "YearBorn": "1971"}, "4": {"Name": "Mr. Manuel Dupla Marin", "Title": "Chief Compliance Officer", "YearBorn": "1970"}, "5": {"Name": "Mr. Francisco Blanco Garcia", "Title": "General Counsel", "YearBorn": "NA"}, "6": {"Name": "Ms. Eugenia  de la Torriente Larranaga", "Title": "Chief Communications Officer", "YearBorn": "1981"}, "7": {"Name": "Ms. Marine Sophie De Boucaud", "Title": "Chief Human Resources Officer", "YearBorn": "1969"}, "8": {"Name": "Mr. Josep  Vivas Carmen", "Title": "Chief Sustainability Officer", "YearBorn": "NA"}, "9": {"Name": "Mr. Marc  Toulemonde", "Title": "President of Derma", "YearBorn": "1974"}}, "Phone": "34 934 00 70 00", "WebURL": "https://www.puig.com", "LogoURL": "", "FullTimeEmployees": 11530, "UpdatedAt": "2026-04-14"}, "Highlights": {"MarketCapitalization": 14682892288, "MarketCapitalizationMln": 14682.8923, "EBITDA": 963990016, "PERatio": 15.5806, "PEGRatio": 2.8055, "WallStreetTargetPrice": 11.5739, "BookValue": 4.0406, "DividendShare": 0, "DividendYield": 0.0226, "EarningsShare": 0.62, "EPSEstimateCurrentYear": 0.54, "EPSEstimateNextYear": 0.59, "EPSEstimateNextQuarter": 0, "EPSEstimateCurrentQuarter": 0, "MostRecentQuarter": "2025-12-31", "Profit